<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/OSC_Microbio_12_02_Ribotyping.jpg"/>
</media>
<caption>A gel showing PCR products of various <emphasis effect="italics">Clostridioides difficile</emphasis> strains. Javier’s sample is shown at the bottom; note that it matches ribotype 27 in the reference set. (credit: modification of work by American Society for Microbiology)</caption>
</figure>
